                        <interp inst="t17541204-4-person52" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , on the 8th of July, about the hour of 2 in the night on the same day, the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17541204-4-victim54" type="victimName">
                           Susannah 
