                        <interp inst="t17541204-4-victim57" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                      
                  , one other note payable to the governor and company of the Bank of England, for 60 l. payable to a person unknown, being then unsatisfied for, and 20 guineas the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17541204-4-victim59" type="victimName">
                           George 
                           Holland 
                        <interp inst="t17541204-4-victim59" type="surname" value="Holland"></interp>
